item.title: CVE-2023-0220|2024-08-02T05:02:44.041Z -- unknown -- pinpoint%20booking%20system
item.description: The Pinpoint Booking System WordPress plugin before 2.9.9.2.9 does not validate and escape one of its shortcode attributes before using it in a SQL statement, which could allow any authenticated users, such as subscriber to perform SQL Injection attacks.
